B.R.I.G.o.F
Brain Rot Internet Game of Fame

Each player presents a tiktok, or reel to the group. After watching player rate the video from 1-5 utils.
1 => Bad, 5 => Great.

Player with the most utils at the end of the round wins 2pts!
    *Players show 3 videos per round.
The Player in second place gets 1pt at the end of the round!

The players in the last two places are shunned. Players remain shunned until they finish a drink. If a player
interacts with the shunned, they are shunned as well.

Player play the game 3 times (sharing a total of 9 videos each), keeping their utils from the previouis rounds.
    *Player with the most utils at the end of the 3 Games gets 1 ZORK.
     If players are tied, they play in a flash round to determine the winner.

